&lt;p&gt;The common thread is simple:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Find growth. Prove it. Scale it.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will report directly to the VP Growth &amp;amp; Marketing and work as a peer to the Director of Brand Marketing &amp;amp; Demand and the Growth Intelligence Strategist.&lt;/p&gt;
